    h4 Loki brings a new API for Wingpanel, Launcher API support in Slingshot, new widgets like AlertView, new CSS style classes and icons, and tons more. Build feature-full apps easier than ever with Gtk 3.18 &amp; Vala 0.32, running atop Linux 4.4

  div.grid
    div.half
      div.alert.column: img(src='https://elementary.io/images/icons/actions/48/document-export.svg')
      div.alert.column
        h2 Contractor
        p A desktop-wide extension service that allows apps to use functionality exposed by other apps â€” without prior coordination.
        p: a(href='https://elementary.io/docs/human-interface-guidelines#contractor').read-more HIG for Contractor
        p: a(href='http://valadoc.org/#!api=granite/Granite.Services.ContractorProxy', target='_blank').read-more Reference for Contractor
    div.half
      div.alert.column: img(src='https://elementary.io/images/developer/granite.svg')
      div.alert.column
        h2 Granite
        p The foundation library for elementary OS apps. Provides powerful widgets like DynamicNotebook, utilities, convenience functions, and more.
        p: a(href='http://valadoc.org/#!wiki=granite/index', target='_blank').read-more Reference for Granite
    div.half
      div.alert.column: img(src='https://elementary.io/images/icons/mimes/48/office-database.svg')
      div.alert.column
        h2 GDA
        p Simple, flexible database management. Supports remote and on-disk SQL databases, including SQLite. Comes with graphical and in-console SQL data browsers, a metadata extractor enabling object auto-discovery, and more.
        p: a(href='http://valadoc.org/#!api=libgda-4.0/Gda', target='_blank').read-more Reference for GDA
    div.half
      div.alert.column: img(src='https://elementary.io/images/icons/categories/48/preferences-system-network.svg')
      div.alert.column
        h2 Soup
        p An HTTP client/server library with synchronous and async APIs. Comes with SSL/TLS, cookies, caching, WebSockets, proxy and tunneling support, and more. Goes great with JSON-GLib.
        p: a(href='http://valadoc.org/#!api=libsoup-2.4/Soup', target='_blank').read-more Reference for Soup
        p: a(href='http://valadoc.org/#!api=json-glib-1.0/Json', target='_blank').read-more Reference for JSON-GLib

  section.grey
    div.grid: div.two-thirds
      img(src='https://elementary.io/images/developer/vala.svg')
      h2 Vala. A Modern, Fast, Open Source Language.
    div.grid
      div.third
        i.fa.fa-cube
        p Familiar to anyone who's seen C#, but maintains API/ABI compatibility with C
      div.third
        i.fa.fa-rocket
        p Low memory requirements, native execution, and purpose-built for GObject
      div.third
        i.fa.fa-cogs
        p Signals, properties, generics, lambdas, assisted memory management, exception handling, type inference, async/yield & more
    div.grid: div.two-thirds
      pre.
        <code>public class MyApp: Gtk.Application {

            public MyApp () {
                Object (application_id: "com.github.myteam.myapp",
                flags: ApplicationFlags.FLAGS_NONE);
            }

            protected override void activate () {
                var window = new Gtk.ApplicationWindow (this);
                window.title = "MyApp";
                window.set_default_size (1024, 768);
                window.show_all ();
            }

            public static int main (string[] args) {
                var app = new MyApp ();
                return app.run (args);
            }
        }</code>
      div.grid
        div.half: a(href="https://wiki.gnome.org/Projects/Vala").read-more Learn More about Vala
        div.half: a(href="http://valadoc.elementary.io").read-more Library Documentation for Vala
